\c 3
\s Vakadzi navarume
\p
\v 1 Saizvozvo imwi vakadzi, \add ivai\add* pasi pavarume venyu; kuti kana varipo vamwe vasingateereri shoko, vawanikwe nomufambire wavakadzi pasina shoko,
\v 2 kana vachivona mufambire wenyu wakachena pakutya.
\v 3 Kushonga kwenyu ngakurege kuva kokunze, kokuruka vhudzi, nokushonga ndarama, kana kupfeka nguwo;
\v 4 asi \add ngakuve\add* munhu wakavanzika wemoyo pazvinhu zvisingaori zvomweya munyoro wakanyarara, unokosha zvikuru pamberi paMwari.
\v 5 Nokuti saizvozvovo panguva dzakare vakadzi vatsvenewo vaivimba naMwari vakazvishongedza vakazviisa pasi pavarume vavo,
\v 6 saSara wakateerera Abhurahamu achimuidza ishe; vakunda vake vamuri imwi kana muchingoita zvakanaka chete, musingatyiswi nechipi nechipi chinovhundusa.
\v 7 Saizvozvo imwi varume, garisanai noruzivo, muchikudza mukadzi semudziyo usina simba, uye savadyi venhaka yenyasha youpenyu pamwe chete \add nemwi\add*; kuti minyengetero yenyu irege kudziviridzwa.
\s Rudo nokutsungirira pakutambudzika
\p
\v 8 Pakupedzisira, \add muve\add* nomoyo mumwe mose, munzwirane ngoni, mudanane sehama, muve nomoyo munyoro, mune rudo;
\v 9 musingatsivi zvakaipa nezvakaipa, kana kutuka nokutuka; asi pakudaro muchiropafadze muchiziva kuti ndizvo zvamakadanirwa, kuti mugare nhaka yeropafadzo.
\v 10 Nokuti uyo unoda upenyu, nokuvona mazuva akanaka, ngaadzore rurimi rwake pane zvakaipa, nemiromo yake kuti irege kutaura zvinonyengera.
\v 11 Ngaanzvenge zvakaipa, aite zvakanaka; ngaatsvake rugare arutevere.
\v 12 Nokuti meso aShe \add ari\add* pamusoro pavakarurama, nenzeve dzake paminyengetero yavo. Asi chiso chaShe \add chiri\add* pamusoro pavanoita zvakaipa.
\v 13 Zvino ndianiko uchakuitirai zvakaipa, kana muri vatevedzeri vezvakanaka?
\v 14 Asi kana muchitambudzika nokuda kokururama, makaropafadzwa; uye musatya kutyisa kwavo, kana kumanikidzika.
\v 15 Asi itai Ishe Mwari mutsvene mumoyo yenyu; mugare makazvigadzira kupindura mumwe nomumwe unokubvunzai pamusoro petariro iri mukati menyu nounyoro nokutya;
\v 16 mune hana yakanaka, kuti pavanokucherai savaiti vezvakaipa vanyare, ivo vanomhura mufambira wenyu wakanaka muna Kristu.
\v 17 Nokuti \add zvi\add*rinani kutambudzika muchiita zvakanaka, kana kuri kuda kwaMwari pa\add kutambudzika\add* muchiita zvakaipa.
\v 18 Nokuti naKristuwo wakatambudzika kamwe nokuda kwezvivi, iye wakarurama nokuda kwavasakarurama, kuti atiise kuna Mwari; wakaurawa zvirokwazvo panyama, asi wakararamiswa nomweya;
\v 19 mauri wakandoparidzirawo mweya iri mutirongo,
\v 20 iyo yaimbova isingateereri, panguva iya moyo murefu waMwari uchimirira pamazuva aNowa apo areka ichagadzirwa; kukaponeswa mairi vashoma, mweya misere nemvura.
\v 21 Mufananidzo wayo ndirwo rubhabhatidzo rwunotiponesa zvino, kwete kubviswa kwesvina yenyama, asi kutsvaka hana yakanaka kuna Mwari nokumukazve kwaJesu Kristu;
\v 22 wakaenda kudenga, uye uri kuruoko rworudyi rwaMwari; vatumwa namadzishe namasimba zvakaiswa pasi pake.
